{"id": 6575, "title": "Ticket #6575: Improve error handling when proxy delegation fails", "description": "<blockquote>\nOur error handling when a proxy delegation over a CEDAR connect fails should be improved.\n\n<p></p><ul>\n<li>Extract and log relevant error messages from the Globus libraries. [Done]\n</li><li>Keep the two sides in sync, so that further communication is possible. [Done]\n</li><li>In file transfer, recognize failures that should put the job on hold (e.g. source file can't be read). [Not done]</li></ul>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2018-May-02 16:14</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/7a6a3f010586bf12085f941ed7989b39d9f806a6\">[54822]</a></span>: Docs for proxy delegation error message improvements. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6575\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6575'); return false;\" title=\"Improve error handling when proxy delegation fails\">#6575</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2018-Feb-21 09:55</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/b3b29d5ca659013bf4d1693450d630b5d1ba3b79\">[54340]</a></span>: Ifdef new globus code and fix new memory leak with globus error message <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6575\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6575'); return false